        | #[strong Red]: banners, shield’s stripes, berries, eagle’s tongue <br>
        | #[strong Gold]: rays, stars, banner’s scroll, eagle’s eye <br>
        | #[strong Yellow]: eagle’s claws <br>
        | #[strong Yellow-Green]: olive leaves <br>
        | #[strong Green]: olive branch and leaves <br>
        | #[strong Medium Blue]: shield’s chief, “North Dakota” <br>
        | #[strong Silver]: eagle’s feathers, arrowheads #4-5 <br>
        | #[strong Dark Brown]: eagle’s feathers, arrow tails, arrowhead #7 <br>
        | #[strong Medium Brown]: eagle’s feathers, arrowhead #6 <br>
        | #[strong Tan]: eagle’s feathers, arrowheads #1-3 <br>
        | #[strong White]: shield’s stripes, eagle’s eye<br>
        | #[strong Black]: eagle’s nose and eye
